| `DB_PORT`            | _Number_  | Database port                                     | `<%= dialect.port %>`  |                                                                                                           |
| `DB_NAME`            | _String_  | Database name                                     |         |                                                                                                                          |
| `DB_USER`            | _String_  | Database user                                     |         |                                                                                                                          |
